data.description:
Nestled in the heart of the highly desirable Wellington community, 3036 Payson Way exudes a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. From the moment you step through the door, you'll be greeted by a meticulously designed living space, flooded with natural light. This open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal environment for both family gatherings and entertaining. The chef's kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring top-of-the-line appliances and granite countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen, a cozy breakfast nook offers a delightful spot to start your day.The master suite is a private sanctuary, boasting an opulent en-suite bathroom and a generous walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms provide ample accommodation for f family or guests. Step outside to your own backyard oasis, complete with a covered patio - perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation. The expansive yard offers plenty of room for a pool, gardening, or play.
Additionally, the home features soaring ceilings, premium finishes throughout, and a three-car garage. 
As for the community, it offers an array of amenities that cater to an active lifestyle. The clubhouse hosts indoor and outdoor basketball courts, pickleball, volleyball, and tennis courts. There's an impressive fitness center and a newly renovated, spacious playground with astroturf and a variety of engaging equipment for children. Low HOA dues cover high-speed ATT internet, four manned security entrances, 24-hour rovers, and more. The sense of community here is truly wonderful.
Furthermore, this home is conveniently located within walking distance to the clubhouse, restaurants, and shopping. Phipps Village, one of the newest sections in Olympia, is a premier estate section known for its exceptional amenities and prime location. And let's not forget the top A-rated Wellington schools that are an added bonus for families. Come see this home in person - it's just as stunning as it appears in these photos. You deserve to live the Olympia lifestyle; now is the time to turn that dream into a reality.
